name: SUPA Foundation
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
SUPA Foundation is an NFT based PVP-style Play-To-Earn game set in an alternate futuristic expansive metaverse.

We will be launching our $SUPA token soon, followed by our NFTs.

In the meantime, follow Supa Foundation's storyline on Discord and install the App to collect SupaFuel Tokens (later claimable in-game).
